*[[August 2]], [[2005]] <U+2013> Traded by the [[Edmonton Oilers]] with [[Jeff Woywitka]] and [[Doug Lynch]] to the [[St. Louis Blues (hockey)|St. Louis Blues]] for [[Chris Pronger]]

